---
// SimulatorSection.astro
---
<section>
    <div class="callout">
        Paint a floor plan below and drag the router around — the signal overlay updates
        live as you edit. Switch between generation tabs to compare coverage. Pay
        attention to how
        <strong>5 GHz generations (Wi‑Fi 2 and Wi‑Fi 5)</strong> sacrifice range for
        speed, and how newer generations maintain stronger coverage through the same
        walls.
    </div>
    <p>
        <em>
            The simulator covers Wi‑Fi 1 through Wi‑Fi 6E. Wi‑Fi 7 (802.11be) is not
            yet modeled. Grid ratio: 1 cell = 1 meter (40 × 30 m space).
        </em>
    </p>
    <slot />
</section>